{"tid":910029,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[壹傳媒喜訊]沈大師評無持續經營能力 難以搵到白武士打救","createTime":"2018-11-21T00:24:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-21T02:30:18.000Z","uid":64874,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2e5fc0d3f7a5c777ebebe62763c453d8e1534b91","tid":910029,"uid":64874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T00:24:09.000Z","msg":"今日因報a22版再為壹傳媒指點迷津，內文重點如下：<br />\n<br />\n壹傳媒賣當借度日 財金界批死 日子餘無幾<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20181121/00176_027.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181121%2F00176_027.html&d=urbJlywAQcMBFL9ikkylnpzN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=9ca34df2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20181121/00176_027.html</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄第二三段<br />\n<br />\n「唔捱得好耐」無持續經營能力<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">訊匯證券行政總裁沈振盈</span>坦言，壹傳媒一年虧蝕總額高達4億元，上述出售實際<span style=\"color: red;\">套現的資金</span>，估計只夠<span style=\"color: red;\">「頂得兩三個月」</span>。未來如要新資金繼續經營，應該「有嘢賣得就賣」。然而，公司能出售的重大資產似乎所餘無幾。<br />\n<br />\n他說，雖然公司仍有若干台灣物業可售，但相信有關物業已抵押予銀行換取融資，實際套現可用的資金將大打折扣。考慮到公司<span style=\"color: red;\">經營前景極不明朗，加上旗下業務不斷燒錢，他認為很難找到「白武士」或新投資者入股打救。</span>"},{"pid":"7f5ce3e1d3a4a79857fdf9228382ba065c1a0548","tid":910029,"uid":56698,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T01:07:15.000Z","msg":"原本仲諗住上網睇蘋果幫手撳吓廣告<br />\n有沈大師加持 今次收購埋其他報紙都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa85e5cc09e91e660f1522dcc3301716358e7ac0","tid":910029,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T01:11:17.000Z","msg":"認真想知蘋果點捱落去"},{"pid":"2e4eac206213f05a20d218114b360b8a5ebe7a21","tid":910029,"uid":17866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa85e5cc09e91e660f1522dcc3301716358e7ac0","tid":910029,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T01:11:17.000Z","msg":"認真想知蘋果點捱落去"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T01:35:45.0